          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center card-shadow">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-rp-blue">🔍 Descubrimiento</h3>
